quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  12,87,beta ( yun karo ke aik dafaa phir ) jao aur Yousuf aur is ke bhai ko talaash karo aur khuda ki rehmat se na umeed nah ho. ke khuda ki rehmat se be imaan log na umeed howa karte hain
  12,88,jab woh Yousuf ke paas gay to kehnay lagey ke Aziz hamein aur hamaray ahal vayal ko barri takleef ho rahi hai aur hum thora sa sarmaya laaye hain aap hamein ( is ke aiwz ) poora Ghalla day dijiye aur khairaat kijiye. ke khuda khairaat karne walon ko sawab deta hai
  12,89,( Yousuf ne ) kaha tumhe maloom hai jab tum nadani mein phansay hue they to tum ne Yousuf aur is ke bhai ke sathkiyakiya tha
  12,90,woh bolaykiya tum hi Yousuf ho? unhon ne kaha haan mein hi Yousuf hon. aur ( Binyamin ki taraf ishara karkay kehnay lagey ) yeh mera bhai hai khuda ne hum par bara ahsaankiya hai. jo shakhs khuda se darta aur sabr karta hai to khuda naiko karon ka ajar zaya nahi karta
  12,91,woh bolay khuda ki qasam khuda ne tum ko hum par fazeelat bakhsh hai aur be shak hum khatakaar they
  12,92,( Yousuf ne ) kaha ke aaj ke din se tum par kuch Atab ( وملامت ) nahi hai. khuda tum ko maaf kere. aur woh bohat reham karne wala hai
  12,93,yeh mera kurta le jao aur usay waalid sahib ke munh par daal do. woh Beena ho jayen ge. aur apne tamam ahal vayal ko mere paas le aao
  12,94,aur jab qaafla ( misar se ) rawana howa to un ke waalid kehnay lagey ke agar mujh ko yeh nah kaho ke ( boorha ) behak gaya hai to mujhe to Yousuf ki bo aa rahi hai
  12,95,woh bolay ke wallah aap isi qadeem ghalti mein ( mubtala ) hain
